ge;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「要死一起死」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5341e4a50e2fb0e4a06f86584123b1d95d840345","tid":1846791,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:39:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>抗疫保命<br />\n推翻政權</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e468f459c195325d3b1de3ffcf925ea715b285ad","tid":1846791,"uid":300782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T23:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}